{"word":"G4934 - συντίθεμαι - syntíthemai - soon-tith'-em-ahee - Agree","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντίθεμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syntíthemai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-tith'-em-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Agree</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உடன்படு, இசை, கட்டுப்பாடு செய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to place in one's mind, resolve, determine; to make an agreement, to engage"},{"paragraph":"2. to assent to, to agree to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; to <i>place jointly</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>consent</i> (<i>bargain</i>, <i>stipulate</i>), <i>concur:</i> - agree assent, covenant.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}